casebody.data:
Rehearing Denied.

No. 77. No. 119. No. 488. No. 301, Misc. No. 316, Misc. Solesbee v. Balkcom, Warden, ante, p. 9; Wissner et al. v. Wissner, 338 U. S. 655; National Maritime Union of America et al. v. National Labor Relations Board, 338 U. S. 954; Tate v. Heinze, Warden, 338 U. S. 956; and Story v. Burford, Warden, 338 U. S. 951.

The petitions for rehearing in these cases are severally denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
